OL,3,C'Welcome to Polos' - sweet shop drugs
OL,4,Cgang who flaunted lavish lifestyles
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FEleven people involved in a sweet shop
OL,8,Fbranded drug line operating from an
OL,9,Fupmarket town in the Cotswolds have
OL,10,Fbeen jailed.
OL,12,FThe 'Polo' drugs line was run like a
OL,13,Fconfectionary business - but instead
OL,14,Fof sweets, the group were selling
OL,15,FClass A drugs.
OL,17,FA voicemail service was even set up to
OL,18,Fpick up missed customer calls, giving
OL,19,Fthe greeting 'welcome to Polos Sweets
OL,20,Fand Confectionary, thank you for
OL,21,Fcalling'.
