OL,3,C'Welcome to Polos' - sweet shop drugs
OL,4,Cgang who flaunted lavish lifestyles
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FHassanjee chose 'Polo' as the name for
OL,8,Fthe drugs line as it was also his
OL,9,Fnickname. Police say he used it to his
OL,10,Fadvantage, creating a brand which sold
OL,11,Fto 300 customers he could recognise
OL,12,Fand trust.
OL,14,FGloucester Crown Court heard
OL,15,FHassanjee's group would earn as much
OL,16,Fas #7,000 a day by sourcing bulk
OL,17,Fquantities of heroin and cocaine and
OL,18,Fselling it on.
