OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FHassanjee, 33, used his riches to fund
OL,8,Fluxury holidays in Asia, designer
OL,9,Fwatches and champagne baths.
OL,11,FHe even paid for his network of
OL,12,Fdealers to live in and work out of
OL,13,Fhigh-end apartments in Cheltenham.
OL,15,FDet Insp Matt Phillips, of
OL,16,FGloucestershire Police said: "Mr
OL,17,FHassanjee led a lifestyle (where) he
OL,18,Fvery much enjoyed the trappings of
OL,19,Fthat; buying Rolex watches, travelling
OL,20,Fabroad.
