OL,7,F"I don't think he was someone who
OL,8,Fsaved an awful lot for a rainy day -
OL,9,Fhe lived off the money he was making."
OL,11,FOften, bosses of drug gangs set up
OL,12,Ftheir dealers in cheap, shabby
OL,13,Faccommodation. But Polo spread his
OL,14,Fwealth, renting at least 11 separate
OL,15,Fhigh-end apartments in this upmarket
OL,16,Ftown for his dealers like Bradley
OL,17,FMcPhee.
