OL,7,FIn one video he filmed of himself,
OL,8,FMcPhee boasted: "Man's living like a
OL,9,Fking bro, literally, that's what it
OL,10,Ffeels like I'm not even joking bro."
OL,12,FHe also referred to himself as "the
OL,13,Fbiggest grafter you'll ever see".
OL,15,FDet Insp Phillips said: "He
OL,16,F(Hassanjee) would book nice flats for
OL,17,Fthem and put them in nice parts of
OL,18,Ftown and even buy them electric
OL,19,Fscooters to drive around on when
OL,20,Fthey're delivering their drugs."
