OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FIn September 2022, police detained the
OL,8,Fthree men who appeared to be dealing
OL,9,Fdrugs. Searches of the property
OL,10,Funcovered a total of 60.27g of crack
OL,11,Fcocaine worth #4,500 and 153.1g of
OL,12,Fheroin worth #3,560. Cash was counted
OL,13,Fand found to total #2,651.76.
OL,15,FIn October 2022, a further runner, 21-
OL,16,Fyear-old Hassan Ahmed, was identified
OL,17,Fto be working for Hassanjee in
OL,18,FCheltenham while under supervision of
OL,19,FKazi Ahmed.
