OL,7,FPolice intercepted a taxi as it
OL,8,Fentered Cheltenham and found Kazi
OL,9,FAhmed inside with 19-year-old Emily
OL,10,FBarbosa. There was a bag of Class A
OL,11,Fdrugs in the boot.
OL,13,FThe bag contained a block of heroin
OL,14,Fweighing 248g, and 37.7g of cocaine
OL,15,Fcompacted into a solid with some
OL,16,Fresidual powder. An additional 26.3g
OL,17,Fof cocaine, which had been divided
OL,18,Finto 39 wraps making a total of 64g,
OL,19,Fwas found in Kazi Ahmed's coat pocket.
