OL,7,FPolice say the group was making around
OL,8,F#7,000 a day from dealing Class A
OL,9,Fdrugs - meaning the enterprise was
OL,10,Fworth hundreds of thousands of pounds
OL,11,Ffor those in charge.
OL,13,FSameer Khan, 20, was one of
OL,14,FHassanjee's trusted drivers -
OL,15,Ftransporting the group between
OL,16,FLeicester and Cheltenham and driving
OL,17,Fpeople to deliver drugs. By the time
OL,18,Fhe was arrested, his involvement had
OL,19,Fstopped with the group.
